These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, coffee, lemonade, tea
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, game, vegafina, pall-mall, dannemann
There are 5 different nationalities: british, chinese, egyptian, malaysian, turkish
5 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, lizard, rabbit, rat
 1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 2. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 3. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the owner of the bird is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 7. the british is on the left of the egyptian##1
 8. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
11. the person drinking tea is between the chinese and the dannemann-smoker##2
12. the malaysian is on the left of the game-smoker##1
13. the turkish is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | 7up        | almond-milk | tea     | coffee   | lemonade |
| Cigar   | vegafina     | game      | pall-mall | dannemann   | bluemaster    |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | chinese     | british | egyptian | turkish  |
| Pet           | chinchilla | lizard      | rat     | rabbit   | bird     |

