 1. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person who's sport is cricket##2
 2. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 3. the fan of d&b is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 4. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 7. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 9. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
10. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the train is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's hobby is reading##2
12. the fan of classical is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
13. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Music-Genre    | disco       | classical    | trance | d&b  | blues        |
| Hobby       | video-games | card-games | reading  | traveling | drawing    |
| Sport       | golf        | handball   | cricket  | sailing   | basketball |
| Transport   | trike       | train      | van      | motorbike | quad-bike  |

